                    <div class="item" style="background-image: url('/media/4216/institute-for-cyber-security.jpg');">
                        <a href="https://www.royalholloway.ac.uk/research-and-teaching/departments-and-schools/information-security/news/doctoral-training-in-cyber-security-receives-more-funding/">
                            <div class="container">
                                <div class="featureTextArea science">
                                    <h2 class="smallText"></h2>
                                    <h3 class="heading3">Doctoral training in Cyber Security receives more funding</h3>
                                    <p class="introText"><p>The UK Engineering and Physical Sciences Research Council (EPSRC) has announced that it is renewing support for the Centre for Doctoral Training in Cyber Security (CDT) at Royal Holloway, University of London, as part of the UK Governmentâs strategy to increase the number of highly trained cyber security experts</p></p>
                                </div>
